HEADWORD: Onappo
<hw>O*nap"po</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A nocturnal South American monkey (<spn>Callithrix discolor</spn>),
noted for its agility; -- called also <altname>ventriloquist
monkey</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Once</ent>⟦br⟧
